snippet.title: Castle Warriors - Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
RTS Roguelike inspired by Starcraft and Vampire Survivors!

Castle Warriors is a rogue like RTS battler that puts you in a race against time. Fight to conquer the kingdoms, build new army combinations, and collect gold bounties to build stronger armies! 

Our steam page just went live, check it out! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2135320/Castle_Warriors/

Follow us at:
https://discord.com/invite/BqZPffsfwE
https://twitter.com/CastleWarriors
https://twitter.com/CluckGamesLLC
https://cluck.dev/

This video features Music: By HeatleyBros 
https://youtu.be/aJxxnJxQD8s
